race.comment: FASHIZLEMANIZLE (4) was well backed on debut but couldn't quite get the job done, finishing a close second at Morphettville Parks. Showed good ability there and will no doubt be better for the debut performance. Full of upside and he's ready to go one better. VATICAN ROSE (12) debuts off a sharp trial and although drawn wide, she looks to have the engine to overcome it. Expect market support and a bold run. MADAM MILLY (7) resumes after a long break but her recent trial placing suggests she's tuned up. Last prep, she's better than that. EL EXPLOSIVO (2) didn't fire fresh but has shown glimpses and gets Milnes on. Could surprise.
